Interface Md2CustomCodeTask

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Md2AttributeSetTask, Md2BindTask, Md2CallTask, Md2MapTask, Md2SyncTask, Md2UnbindTask, Md2UnmapTask

    public interface Md2CustomCodeTask
    Interface definition of a custom code task. Custom code tasks are used in custom code actions. Represents task in CustomCodeFragment element in MD2-DSL.
